What we're looking for
For the Data Science and Data Analysis programs, we are looking for an experienced data scientist to review our students and help them successfully become professionals.

Requirements:


Proficient English, Indonesian languages;
Experience working as an analyst using Python;
Experience working with machine learning projects for more than a year;
Familiar with the Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Sklearn libraries;
Readiness to dedicate at least 10 hours a week to review the student code.

